# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [1.0.0] - 2026-04-07

### Added
- Initial release
- Multi-host SSL/TLS certificate monitoring
- Configurable warning thresholds (multiple levels)
- Slack Webhook notification support
- JSON output mode for integration
- Certificate details: subject, issuer, dates, fingerprint, serial
- Status caching to avoid duplicate alerts
- Summary report after each check cycle
- Config file support with inline warning overrides
